Look at https://github.com/lefoyer/vmrefresh

Installing vmrefresh plugin
---------------------------------------

You need roundcube > 1.0 installed.

1. Download the latest version it to the roundcube plugins dir :

    mkdir <path_to_roundcube>/plugins/vmrefresh

    cd <path_to_roundcube>/plugins/vmrefresh

    git clone https://github.com/lefoyer/vmrefresh.git .

2. Add "vmrefresh" to the plugins list in <path_to_roundcube>/config/main.inc.php, for example :

    $rcmail_config['plugins'] = array('vmrefresh',);

It works :)


Configuration
-------------

You can customize some settings :

    copy config.inc.php.dist to config.inc.php
    edit config.inc.php as you fancy
